paragraph.def:
the term “international
                        traffic” means any carriage by an aircraft except when such carriage
                    is solely between places in the area of the other Contracting Party;

subsection.leadIn:
This Article shall enter into force on the date of the last written notification
                confirming that the Contracting Parties have fulfilled all the internal procedures
                for the entry into force of this Article and the Article shall be applied:

paragraph.content:
in the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region, for any year of assessment
                    beginning on or after 1st April in the calendar year next following that in
                    which this Article enters into force;

in the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region, for any year of assessment
                    beginning on or after 1st April in the calendar year next following that in
                    which the notice of termination is given;
